content: Give a numbered list of several Russian symbolist poets who created in early XXth century.

chosen:
Here is a list of several Russian symbolist poets who created in the early 20th century:

1. Aleksandr Blok (1880-1921)
2. Vladimir Mayakovsky (1893-1930)
3. Sergei Yesenin (1895-1925)
4. Anna Akhmatova (1889-1966)
5. Boris Pasternak (1890-1960)
6. Marina Tsvetaeva (1892-1941)
7. Osip Mandelstam (1891-1938)
8. Nikolai Gumilev (1886-1921)
9. Velimir Khlebnikov (1885-1922)
10. Fyodor Sologub (1863-1927)
